Oversized lot, 7 yr. old roof, & an iron gate & fence for added security. HUGE luxurious primary bath, vaulted ceilings, abundant natural lighting, & skylights. SPACIOUS living room offers a stunning view of the lake —perfect for peaceful living. Make this one yours and schedule your showing today!
